(Q)Display names of all the instructors concatenated wuth their department names.
select i.name || '-' || d.name from instructor i join department d on i.dept_id=d.dept_id;

I.NAME||'-'||D.NAME
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
John Doe-Computer Science
